程序包 org.elasticsearch.painless.node

接口 SSource.Reserved

  • 所有已知实现类:
    SFunction.FunctionReserved, SSource.MainMethodReserved
    封闭类:
    SSource
    public static interface SSource.Reserved
    Tracks derived arguments and the loop counter. Must be given to any source of input prior to beginning the analysis phase so that reserved variables are known ahead of time to assign appropriate slots without being wasteful.
